The ⠀⠀ of Nooooooooooooooo is a colossal, genial nation, ruled by John Edwards with an even hand, and renowned for its museums and concert halls, anti-smoking policies, and restrictive gun laws. The compassionate, democratic, cheerful population of 9.769 billion Noons are fiercely patriotic and enjoy great social equality; they tend to view other, more capitalist countries as somewhat immoral and corrupt.

The government — a sprawling, bureaucracy-choked morass — juggles the competing demands of Education, Administration, and Healthcare. It meets to discuss matters of state in the capital city of Salabrachon. The average income tax rate is 97.4%.

The frighteningly efficient Noon economy, worth a remarkable 1,279 trillion Angorejes a year, is driven entirely by a combination of government and state-owned industry, with private enterprise illegal. The industrial sector, which is highly specialized, is mostly made up of the Information Technology industry, with significant contributions from Book Publishing. Average income is an impressive 131,010 Angorejes, and distributed extremely evenly, with little difference between the richest and poorest citizens.

Court verdicts are predictable to within a hundredth of a percentage point, the bonfire of the old paper records can be seen for miles around Salabrachon, there's a lot of mouth-breathers about these days, and companies struggle to cover for the hordes of employees on parental leave. Crime, especially youth-related, is totally unknown, thanks to a well-funded police force and progressive social policies in education and welfare. Nooooooooooooooo's national animal is the foster, which frolics freely in the nation's many lush forests.

Nooooooooooooooo is ranked 2,753rd in the world and 1st in Callista for Healthiest Citizens, with 24.88 bananas ingested per day.

The Socialist Empire of Communist Beijing Must be China is a massive, cultured nation, ruled by Sir Helmeiner V with an even hand, and notable for its triple-decker prams, complete lack of prisons, and ubiquitous missile silos. The compassionate, devout population of 1.908 billion Cabemkians have some civil rights, but not too many, enjoy the freedom to spend their money however they like, to a point, and take part in free and open elections, although not too often.

The medium-sized, corrupt government juggles the competing demands of Administration, Education, and Healthcare. It meets to discuss matters of state in the capital city of Degradja-Snadja-Kavren. The average income tax rate is 69.4%, and even higher for the wealthy.

The frighteningly efficient Cabemkian economy, worth 265 trillion Sen Paiers a year, is fairly diversified and led by the Arms Manufacturing industry, with major contributions from Information Technology, Tourism, and Trout Farming. Black market activity is rampant. State-owned companies are common. Average income is an impressive 138,963 Sen Paiers, and evenly distributed, with the richest citizens earning only 2.2 times as much as the poorest.

Relations with Dàguó have warmed from frosty to chilly, raindances intended to summon storms instead attract tourists, the minority inevitably have their addenda vetoed, and matryoshka dolls resembling nested Death Stars are commonly sold. Crime, especially youth-related, is totally unknown. Communist Beijing Must be China's national animal is the Hamzilistamdog, which is also the nation's favorite main course, and its national religion is Krovichism.
